name: Over Packed
description:
Game created by Programmer https://twitter.com/leehammoud and Artisthttps://twitter.com/cyborgette.

The goal of the game is get packing for your next travel. (Even if borders are closed, but nobody knows that.) Grab, aim and shoot your travel essentials to the evil suitcase in your main bedroom. 

You can't use doors! Oh no. No, no. Destroy your house foundation with the very couch you rest on, and kick down those walls to the rooms in your house to find the missing items. 

Easy, right? Except there's a timer! Crew captain will not wait for you. Get fast and furiously frustrated with OverPacked! A wonderful physics-frenzied game with a timer to rush through your errands. 

Cheers, and hope you enjoy it all!
